name: Enttoi
body:
### Welcome to Enttoi

Enttoi is system that collects sensors data, push them to centralized place, which allows to see their state in real-time and gather statistics.

### Building blocks

The entire solution consists on number of repositories, which can be found [here](https://github.com/Enttoi). The building procedures for each repository located in *readme.md* file within repositories.
